@faz3 @groupfazza 🙏

Your Highness Sheikh Hamdan,
Mothers come to leaders for justice when their children are taken from them. In this case, a mother’s children were abducted, and false statements were placed before Dubai courts to conceal the truth. We ask only for justice and your diplomatic assistance so that lies do not prevail over the rights of a mother and her children.

With faith in truth, we believe Dubai courts will, under your guidance, return custody and guardianship to the mother and restore the children to their rightful place.

Allah keep you, your family and nation blessed and secure.

